&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit new qualified and established Band 5 Operating Department Practitioners to join our busy theatre department, undertaking anaesthetics as the majority of their workload.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We undertake a number of specialties including ENT, Maxillo- facial, Gynaecology, Bariatrics, Trauma and Orthopaedics along with numerous others.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Successful applicants will be fully supported through a preceptorship programme.&lt;/p&gt;
